trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView"></xref> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView"> </xref> Web serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control renders one of its templates, determined by whether a user is logged on to the host Web site, and the roles that contain the logged-on user account.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontrollen gjengir én av de malene, avhenger av om en bruker er logget på webområdet vert og roller som inneholder den påloggede brukeren-kontoen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning markup kildekode som beskriver den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The LoginViewDesigner class provides design-time support for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen LoginViewDesigner gir støtte for utforming for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.ActionLists%2A> property returns a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> object, which typically contains an object that is derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> class for each level in the inheritance tree of the designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.ActionLists%2A>returnerer en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>objektet, som vanligvis inneholder et objekt som er avledet av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>klasse for hvert nivå i treet arving av designer.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.ActionLists%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> property returns a collection of template groups for the templates of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>egenskapen returnerer en samling av malen grupper for malene for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property always returns `true`, indicating that the designer creates a temporary copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>egenskapen returnerer alltid `true`, som angir at det opprettes en midlertidig kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontrollen til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The LoginViewDesigner class methods provide the following functionality: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> methods return the markup that is used to render the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control at design time.

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.GetEditableDesignerRegionContent%2A> method returns a serialized copy of the current template for the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control.

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.Initialize%2A> method prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control.
trans-unit.target: - <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.Initialize%2A>Metoden Klargjør utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A> method is called when there is a change to the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>metoden kalles når det er en endring i den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.OnComponentChanged%2A>

trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A>metoden brukes til å fjerne egenskaper fra, Legg til flere egenskaper i eller skyggelegge egenskapene for den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LoginViewDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A>

trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml formaterer først en Strengemelding som angir navnet på gjeldende mal for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontrollere og angir også at malen er tom.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> that provides the name of the region to update.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> som inneholder navnet på området til å oppdatere.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains a serialized template for the associated control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder en serialisert mal for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups for the fields of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av malen grupper for feltene for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property gets a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> object from the TemplateGroups base property, and then adds <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> objects that contain a single <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> object for the anonymous template (which corresponds to no user logged on), for the logged-on template, and for each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RoleGroup> element in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView.RoleGroups%2A> collection of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen TemplateGroups henter et <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>objekt fra egenskapen TemplateGroups base og legger <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>objekter som inneholder ett enkelt <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition>objekt for anonym malen (som samsvarer med noen bruker logget på) for malen som er logget på, og hvert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RoleGroup>element i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView.RoleGroups%2A>samlingen av den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontrollen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView.RoleGroups%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RoleGroup> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateDefinition> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups returns this <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> to the caller.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer TemplateGroups dette <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>til oppkalleren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"></xref> containing an element for each template in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"> </xref> som inneholder et element for hver mal i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control that is associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for den faktiske kontrollen som er forbundet med designer for å generere utformingen markup.

trans-unit.source: Because the UsePreviewControl property is always `true`, the designer <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> property returns a copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Fordi egenskapen UsePreviewControl alltid `true`, designer <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>egenskapen returnerer en kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontrollen til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A> property creates the copy by persisting the actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control, then parsing the persisted control string.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>egenskapen oppretter kopien av persisting den faktiske <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontrollen, og deretter analyse faste kontroll-streng.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner.ViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: The copied control does not affect any persistence for the actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>.
trans-unit.target: Kopierte kontrollen påvirker ikke noen utholdenhet for den faktiske <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>

trans-unit.source: If the UsePreviewControl property has been overridden to return `false`, the designer will use the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView> control itself to generate the design-time markup, and design-time changes to the control will persist to the page markup source.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen UsePreviewControl er overstyrt for å returnere `false`, designer bruker den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>kontrollere selve for å generere utformingen markup og utformingen endringer av kontrollen vil beholde siden markup kilde.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LoginView>
